name: Midnight Stroll With Two Friends Named Jolynn And Brian (KAP#37.0)
description: An art day at the McCabes in May, 2021 had 7 year old Jolynn painting this beautiful scene of serenity. She added herself and Brian from school with fine tip marker. Jolynn insisted on the title of this piece. Origins: Alpha. KAP number 37.0. https://linktr.ee/kidartprojects
